snippet.title: Resident Evil 1 (Playstation 1) Original Trailer/Commercial
snippet.description: Ladies and Gentleman, welcome to the Resident Evil Experience, the place for all things Resident Evil/Biohazard. We aim to cover the entire franchise in a multitude of ways, from original commercials, to unique content. If you are a lover of Resident Evil/Biohazard, subscribe today for more future content.
